---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/alert-sprinkler/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Alert Sprinkler Co., Inc.">
  <main style="padding-top: 6rem;" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4" style="color: #291715;">About Alert Sprinkler Co., Inc.</h1>
    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-16" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
      Alert Sprinkler was established in 1977 and incorporated in 1978. We have been serving New Jersey
      and southeastern Pennsylvania for over 45 years. The scope of our work includes engineering, design,
      installation, and reinforcement of fire sprinkler systems. We also perform inspections, tests, repairs,
      and maintenance of sprinkler systems.
    </p>

    <!-- Licensing & Credentials -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #291715;">Licensing &amp; Credentials</h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-base" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
        <li>Fully insured and licensed by the State of New Jersey</li>
        <li><strong>NJ License:</strong> #P01629</li>
        <li>NJ Fire Safety Certification in Fire Sprinkler Systems and Portable Fire Extinguishers</li>
        <li><strong>Certification:</strong> #195457</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Workforce -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #291715;">Our Workforce</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
        We are a union company and all employees have been through a 5-year apprentice program to guarantee
        that their skills meet requirements in the field. We have been fortunate to have had the same core
        of fitters for the last 25+ years. We place a high value on employee loyalty — it enables us to
        give our customers the best possible service.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Management -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #291715;">Management</h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-base" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
        <li>
          <strong style="color: #291715;">Chad Blum</strong> — President
          <br /><a href="mailto:chad@alertsprinkler.com" class="text-as-primary hover:underline">chad@alertsprinkler.com</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong style="color: #291715;">Steve Toth</strong> — Vice President
          <br /><a href="mailto:steve@alertsprinkler.com" class="text-as-primary hover:underline">steve@alertsprinkler.com</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong style="color: #291715;">Taran Fedor</strong> — Office Manager
          <br /><a href="mailto:taran@alertsprinkler.com" class="text-as-primary hover:underline">taran@alertsprinkler.com</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
